unittitle_ssm: New York University Archives Collection of the Square Daily
abstract_ssm: This collection contains issues from the student newspaper the Square Daily dating from April to May 1953.  This newspaper documented student life at NYU (particuarly at the Washington Square campus), local and national news, campus living, and student clubs. The collection is extensive but not comprehensive, there may be some issues that were published but are not included in this collection.
